metadata.description:
The stars glowed bright against the sapphire sky as her long lashes came together and she fell into a deep slumber.  
As she awakened, golden rays of sun caressed her amber-like skin. 
She patted down her companion's soft fur, whispered a hushed word of encouragement...  
And they were off on their never-ending journey. 

This piece is the first dynamic work created by Camibus, changing from night to day as a metaphor for the never-ending journey it represents.
